Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你已經有能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你最後抵達的地方 將是你容身的原野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們是來鬧的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼討厭眼睛能束縛你們手腳的她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她要是想念這個家 自然會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且要把她帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非人類的樣子會更方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為人的生命 比森林之影中誕生的半成品更為脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們都這麼稱呼我 疏遠我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我討厭寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太叫人憐愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好美麗 好快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是…什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彷彿有人在我耳邊叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺自己哪裡都可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甚至是荒無人煙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 因為有人在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想走的話 我陪你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你對那邊已經沒有留念了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是什麼人來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 我還有很多東西不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世不在 我會很頭痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你會頭痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還會很冷 很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不喜歡寒冷 所以我這就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺還迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是詛咒的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}詛咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是變身人狼所用的毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過現在是狐狸皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人狼的毛皮會回應人的訴求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是份不懷好意的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要用得先問過我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他那種人就叫做愉快犯 還跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是我真的去了那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世不想去的話 我會阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算我想也要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
