Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:26.19,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}ほんの一秒を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:30.44,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}ほんの一秒を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:34.13,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}剥がれ堕ちた星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}頬を伝い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:44.00,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}暁を照らした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:42.06,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}光陰的沙海間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:49.50,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:58.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}那柔軟的心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:07.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我卻無法觸及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:15.29,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}愛的熱流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:23.44,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}光著腳跑過身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:32.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}那是我在你的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:39.11,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}追逐著你的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:46.78,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}劃過的風中 帶著砂礫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:55.22,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}如果世界 躲在瓶底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:03.96,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我願倒過瓶口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:14.31,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}無數次 與你描繪明天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.19,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}心愛的半月喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:22.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我還有最後的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:26.19,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}請再給我一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:30.44,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}請再給我一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:34.13,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}滑落的顆顆星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}淌過我臉頰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:44.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}映出了拂曉的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和妻子生死別離以後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就只是為了活而活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但突然有一天 有一刻見到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好美 我好想能再見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就此 我的人生有了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽到這話 我不是更加離不開你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道自己會去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許能到達妻子的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我一定 也一定會去往你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要不孤單 有等候我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就一點都不害怕 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的生命 你就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 我還沒回答你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類真是好笨 好任性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}永遠地等下去 等著喬伊再回到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}悲傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是看到你流眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體裡就會有些不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 不能成為你的教師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 還是快回去躺下休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奧布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精的藥膏 「眼皮上的祝福」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類是不可以做這種藥的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 剩下的能交給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請拿去
Comment: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:33.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:37.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:47.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:57.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:04.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:10.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:16.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:23.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:29.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:36.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:42.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:50.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:33.14,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:37.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:47.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:57.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:04.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:10.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:16.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:23.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只有你在 才有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:29.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們形影不離（形影不離）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:36.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}夢寐以求的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:42.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}屬於我們的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:50.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}我們卻仍在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}觸碰禁忌的代價是那麼沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被死亡的陰影漸漸侵蝕的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然有妖精王一眾相救…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些孩子會越來越衰弱
